titles: An Abstract of some letters sent from Dorchester to some friends in London, dated the 3. of Septem. 1642 containing a true relation of the late proceedings of Marquesse Hartford and the Cavaliers at Sherbon Castle, with the opposition of that and other adjacent counties to those proceedings.
notes: Reproduction of original in Thomason Collection, British Library.
